title: Cant create lobby HELPPP!!!
body:
ayyooo pressed play and all game modes besides tutorial and practice tool have an icon (!) next to them, i hit create lobby and it tells me "something unexpected happened while trying to create your lobby."

now i looked back on other threads that posted the same issue and followed all their instructions ie. restarting internet ect ect
i even did a repair tool on the client and i am still having the same error, i literally played yesterday and didnt have this issue at all!
any help appreciated!
sincerely,
Mawdred.

replies.body:
Things will hopefully be back to normal soon!
